content.title: Kugerwaho Interface Reba
content.howToUseTooltip:
Hano haribiranga ibiranga iyi node ishobora gukoreshwa muguhitamo ibikorwa, nko gukanda, kuzuza inyandiko, nibindi

Ikiranga agaciro kirashobora kwigana kurupapuro rwa porogaramu. Niba uhuye na duplicates, nyamuneka hejuru y'ibindi biranga kugirango umenye umwihariko.

Ijambo ritukura ryerekana ko ikiranga gisubirwamo, ijambo ryicyatsi ryerekana ko ikiranga gisanzwe murupapuro rwubu, kandi ijambo ryirabura ryerekana ko ntagereranywa.
